Projects.Title: Sock Matching
Projects.Description: Developed a machine-learning model that can analyze images of 2 socks to determine if they form a pair. The model was trained using TensorFlow and the model was deployed as a RESTful API using Flask. The front-end was built using React. The model was trained using Convolutional Neural Networks
